    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable vehicle that's ready to get the job done? This car is a solid choice for anyone seeking a functional and honest daily driver! While it shows some clear signs of use and age, it remains a reliable performer that\u2019s perfect for someone who values utility over a perfect finish.",
