    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been preserved with the utmost care. The exterior paint is flawless and retains a deep, mirror-like luster, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, providing a driving experience exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a collector or discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection.",
