    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing a reliable daily driver. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are sound and have been serviced regularly, ensuring the car runs and drives as expected. However, please note that there are visible signs of cosmetic wear, including some paint fading on the hood and minor scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery shows some staining and typical wear for its age, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. It is a solid, honest vehicle that provides good value for someone looking for transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
