    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the meticulously maintained cabin, adheres to the most exacting standards of excellence. This offering represents a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a specimen of uncompromising mechanical and aesthetic integrity.",
